- project: finalproject-tps
- language: typescript, react, react-three-fiber
- added: vertical glass-and-steel center separator at x = 0 colored #eef3f6 to match floor slabs, dividing west (BARAT) and east (TIMUR) elevator banks in BuildingScene.tsx.
- added: dynamic floating billboard passenger count badge above 3D elevator cars inside BuildingScene.tsx when carrying passengers.
- added: interactive, elegant glassmorphic float-overlay zoom in / zoom out controls on the 3D building canvas utilizing OrbitControls ref and a programmatic ZoomController in BuildingScene.tsx.
- optimized: raised BARAT/TIMUR and Utara/Selatan labels to hover gracefully above the roof pergola structure to avoid overlap.
- optimized: increased horizontal spacing between Utara and Selatan labels by offsetting their positions dynamically based on shaft alignment to maximize legibility and layout cleanliness.
- modified: restricted back facade dense architectural vertical fins exclusively to Floor 11, extending standard glass window bays, siding panels, and divide piers up through Floor 10.
- migrated: fully refactored custom vanilla glassmorphism styling into cohesive Tailwind CSS v4 utilities inside App.tsx, ControlPanel.tsx, MetricsPanel.tsx, ChartsPanel.tsx, and BuildingScene.tsx, dramatically simplifying index.css.
- added: Peak-Traffic Mode (Skenario Jam Sibuk) with quick-select glassmorphic preset buttons on ControlPanel.tsx and 90/10 probability trip generators for morning, classChange (lunch), and leaving in passengerGenerator.ts.
- upgraded: global color scheme in index.css to a custom-curated Glacier Slate & Bio Sage High-Tech palette (featuring Glacier Teal `#00decb` and Bio Sage `#10ac84`), eliminating generic standard Tailwind neon tones and elevators SGLC theme integration.
- refactored: transformed entire application shell, navbar, and panels to Dark Neumorphism (Soft UI) using matching backgrounds (#181f2a / #131922) and physical 3D extruded/inset shadow definitions in index.css.
- refactored: updated ControlPanel.tsx with physical neumorphic start/pause/step/reset control buttons and toggleable recessed preset scenarios (Jam Masuk, Jam Makan Siang, Jam Pulang, Normal) without emojis.
- refactored: transformed MetricsPanel.tsx cards into soft extruded neumorphic panels with recessed (inset well) metric indicators, and converted the runtime progress track to a dark inset well.
- refactored: wrapped ChartsPanel.tsx in a beautiful dark inset neumorphic panel container and updated the titles.
- refactored: redesigned the floating zoom overlay capsule in BuildingScene.tsx into a premium neumorphic capsule with double-deck physical push buttons.
- fixed: resolved ChartsPanel.tsx height overflow clipping inside the clamped dashboard bottom grid row by removing duplicate margins and changing min-h to flex-1 min-h-0.
- fixed: adjusted AreaChart left margin from -24 to -12 to prevent Y-axis tick labels from being clipped against the left border of the inset container.
- optimized: cleaned up unused Tailwind classes, compressing CSS bundle size from ~54 kB down to ~37 kB.
